BUY
  Purchase a lot from the open market.

SYNTAX
  buy <lot#> <destination-x,y>

DESCRIPTION
  Buys a lot currently listed on the market (see 'trade' to list
  available lots).  The purchased goods are delivered to the
  specified destination sector.

  <lot#>            - lot number from the 'trade' listing
  <destination-x,y> - where to deliver the goods

  You must have enough money to cover the purchase price.  The
  goods appear in the destination sector after delivery.

  Use 'trade' to see current market listings with lot numbers.

EXAMPLE
  trade                     list available lots
  buy 3 0,0                 buy lot 3, deliver to capital

SEE ALSO
  sell  trade  commodity  nation
